                    <img src="/images/js.png" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Java Script</h5>
                        <p>Spring Start Here is a book by Laurentiu Spilca</p>
                        <a href="/pdf/javascript notes .pdf" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">View Book</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
                    <img src="/images/git.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Git & Github</h5>
